                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The blackfrost prophet concentrates on a creature within 60 feet, filling the target's mind with befuddling susurrations. The creature must succeed at a @Check[type:will|dc:28] save or take @Damage[(4d8+8)[mental]] and become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} for 1 minute (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} on a critical failure). The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} as long as it's stupefied.</p>"
